Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:07.46,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:14.75,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:22.93,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Because I closed my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:28.94,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,and distanced myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:35.70,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,5 PM in the school yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:42.58,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,The ball's shadow is growing tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:50.04,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:53.76,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we meet in the hallway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:58.51,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,we always quarreled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:06.69,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:13.65,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:20.99,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Because I opened my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:27.79,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,and we understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.18,0:01:38.72,eptitle,TITLE,0000,0350,0000,,Episode 6\N\NFine day to\N have ESP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:56.54,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Oh thunderbolts that pirrce through the sky of chaos and shine upon the ocean of possiblity!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:07.42,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,That was the instant that life on Earth was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:15.66,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, life! Create a life out of non-life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.40,Default,-Male-:,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:26.30,Default,-Male-:,0000,0000,0000,,Overseas Carrier Service...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.36,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:36.90,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's from the Voodoo Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:40.20,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... half of my year's allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:49.05,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Solving the mystery of the mask will be the first step to solving the mystery of Voodoo.  And I will do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.50,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, Dawsing is a type of ESP.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:05.45,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,With this power, not only undiscovered mineral deposits, its possible to find undiscovered worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:09.50,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently working on a new method of Dawsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:13.50,Default,kageuS:t,0000,0000,0000,,It does not involve sticks or stones, but the use of human eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:17.15,Default,kageuS:t,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this is clairvoyance.\NAs for how I will use it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:24.20,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,But first, let me explain about clairvoyance.  This has nothing to do with clay, get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:25.92,Default,DaiJoj:,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:29.70,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Daijoji?\NI'll take your questions afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:34.84,Default,DaiJoj:,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind stopping all those fairy tales and get back to the course materials?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.60,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Thats where things get interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:40.18,Default,DaiJoj:,0000,0000,0000,,Its not covered in the text!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:43.92,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!  Do you think this garbage would contain such material?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:47.86,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,I am the only one who knows the truth about the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:50.05,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, so does Matsunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.70,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:54.96,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,About ESP powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.22,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:58.60,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,About the true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:03.66,Default,DaiJoj:,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, will you get back to the course material?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.85,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,You have an interesting flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:13.62,Default,MikaGe:T,0000,0000,0000,,My dad brought it back from overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:16.70,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Want to go eat pafe at "Basha Michi?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:18.54,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sheesh!  Not now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:21.12,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Foreign flower?  That's interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:27.20,Default,kageuS:T,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.77,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,There are certain things she can't wait, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.50,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,This must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:42.22,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:47.28,Default,-Male-:,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in front of the girls' restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:52.20,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask a student in there about paranormal phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:57.20,Default,-Male-:,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of paranormal phenomena exist in girls' restrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:03.50,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:06.80,Default,MikaGe:g,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kageura was asking me about the bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:10.00,Default,TOMoMi:tx,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's take it off for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:15.30,Default,MikaGe:t,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kageura is really pesky.\NAnd I have his class everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:20.80,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's bad enough.\NI really like this flower though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:25.55,Default,TOMoMi:x,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me too.  After all, it syncs with our wavelengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:33.10,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you turn off the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:42.32,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's dish looks very delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.63,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:46.50,Default,KaWIFE:,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget the prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.70,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Heavenly light stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:56.46,Default,-Male-:,0000,0000,0000,,I am Keitaro Asou.\NThe Heavenly light stone stimulate the hidden human power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:06:00.30,Default,-Male-:,0000,0000,0000,,I am convinced that there is a deposit of the mineral in Mount Kongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:01.20,Default,KaWIFE:x,0000,0000,0000,,Lets eat now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.80,Default,-MaleB:x,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not familier with the stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:08.00,Default,-Male-:t,0000,0000,0000,,If it's discovered, it could greatly enhance the development of ESP.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:12.80,Default,KaWIFE:,0000,0000,0000,,Its very rude to stand up during a meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:16.10,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Ah?  I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:50.94,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Juliet, I'm going to find the heavenly light stone deposit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:55.90,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,All it takes is to build a sensor to detect the alpha waves emitted by the stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.54,Default,kageuS:x,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... blah blah
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.24,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Juliet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:05.01,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you to not touch this water?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:11.92,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Juliet, did you bring this for my research fund?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:16.60,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice raven you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:20.35,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Juliet, next time, bring me paper money!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:29.00,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it possible... that I have created a life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:39.44,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Lord.  Forgive me for my talent and intelligence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:46.50,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,More!   More!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:50.20,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,More!   Oh Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.80,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:35.20,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:38.70,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,The voodoo mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.45,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,EH?!  Whats this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.50,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:16.10,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,I see!   I have acquired ESP!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.62,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Now!  Where could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.20,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Found a 100 yen coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:41.66,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,No need for a machine anymore.  I can find the deposit once I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:42.92,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,There's a 500 yen coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:46.90,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Blow harder wind!  Ah!  That's a 10 yen coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:58.22,Default,kageuS:s,0000,0000,0000,,Generally when solid liquid or gas coexist with other phases, one of the phase will exist as minute particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:03.70,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Textbooks are like a bible for students, you shouldn't abuse it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:08.80,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Collided particles are one micron to hundred micron big.  They are bigger than atoms and ions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:13.15,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, are you going to teach chemistry today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:17.50,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,You ask strange questions.  I am a chemistry teacher, why shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.63,Default,DaiJoj:d,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.90,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  My fellow super people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:28.70,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,"Fellow"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.05,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,"Super people"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:38.00,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see why you two tried so hard to hide your powers.  This power is indeed not something to be shown to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:44.00,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,You two look surprised.  I'm telling you, that I now have the same power as you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:46.20,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,Same powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:49.50,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Mine may be stronger than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.50,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Honjitsu TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:06.10,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to get in contact with Keitaro Asou, who was on last night's "Hidden Secrets of the Heavenly Light Stone".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:18.50,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  There is something I want to talk to him about, with the relation between the stone and ESP powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.30,Default,TOMoMi:T,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a trick was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:36.75,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,He was definitely floating and there was no devices around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:39.52,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to believe it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:40.70,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.70,Default,KaWIFE:,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan, dinner time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.00,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:01.22,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:06.00,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,I think this flower looks weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:16.10,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,I hope this will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:19.60,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,Get well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.14,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Listen Lica-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.36,Default,KaWIFE:,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:29.40,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,There is something I want to tell you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:31.75,Default,KaWIFE:,0000,0000,0000,,What could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.70,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that I myself find hard to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:40.20,Default,KaWIFE:,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe there's things you can't believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:44.50,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,I've never imagined this would happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:45.85,Default,KaWIFE:,0000,0000,0000,,You mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:50.60,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  I've become an ESPer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.85,Default,KaWIFE:,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:58.00,Default,KaWIFE:,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what you were going to say, but I'm relieved now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.90,Default,KaWIFE:,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:07.50,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really understand this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:16.00,Default,-Male-:,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, Satsuma and Choshu united the force by the work of a ronin called Ryoma Sakamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:20.30,Default,-Male-:,0000,0000,0000,,And this was the dawn of the modern nation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:05.10,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:09.62,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,May I be excused?  I have a sick friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:14.42,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hand in a permit form tomorrow. Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.12,Default,TOMoMi:d,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:22.40,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're leaving too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:25.30,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.60,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the flowers were crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:46.60,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,Is it dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:48.16,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,No, its not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:51.40,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,But its color has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:55.00,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,Will you shutup?  That's why I'm looking into it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:58.86,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.94,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:12.36,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,Speak to us...  What can we do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.62,Default,KaWIFE:,0000,0000,0000,,Oh stop it, Shin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:29.20,Default,KaWIFE:,0000,0000,0000,,Ya!  More Shin-chan, do more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.20,Default,KaWIFE:T,0000,0000,0000,,More!  More!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.70,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Ya, Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:51.80,Default,KaWIFE:,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Shin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:59.94,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's warm up.  1 2 3 heeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:10.00,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,I should be in good shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:25.18,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be... MOVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:36.50,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Move...!   MOOVE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.80,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,It moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:48.12,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,My god... for a moment, I thought I lost the power.  Thank heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.35,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, can't we rest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:57.80,Default,-Male-:,0000,0000,0000,,Again?  If we don't hurry,\Nwe'll be caught in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.86,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:03.85,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Once I get into the mountain, I'll find it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:05.50,Default,-Male-:,0000,0000,0000,,That's the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:13.38,Default,-Male-:,0000,0000,0000,,Lets see.  This is the tree,\NI found the ore right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:18:01.00,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Thats strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.95,Default,-Male-:t,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.21,Default,-Male-:,0000,0000,0000,,Kageura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.66,Default,-Male-:t,0000,0000,0000,,Kageura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:09.05,Default,TOMoMi:T,0000,0000,0000,,We're being pulled in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:20.10,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,The heavenly light stone is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:02.00,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flying thru the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.50,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,Thats Kageura...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.50,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:24.10,Default,kageuS:o,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!  What?!  Climb up!  Climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:27.90,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,I feel heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.00,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,Weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:41.75,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,It's this stone, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:46.00,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,Yea, the flowers are healthy again!  Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:46.98,Default,MikaGe:d,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:51.40,Default,MikaGe:T,0000,0000,0000,,Did this stone draw us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:03.72,Default,-Male-:,0000,0000,0000,,Kageura-san, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:14.62,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, the healing method whereby the hand contacts with the affected part to provide a cure is seen throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:22.00,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,You have a very nice pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:24.00,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:28.62,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomomi, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:33.50,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Matsunaga!\NLet me see that pendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:34.63,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,Catch!  It's yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:35.65,Default,kageuS:,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:51.04,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,In our next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:52.25,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so drowsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:53.10,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:54.45,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't have enough sleep, we can see future visions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:55.47,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:57.28,Default,MikaGe:,0000,0000,0000,,So, lets stay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:22:01.26,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,Next on Miracle Girls: "Precognition Index? Percent"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:04.00,Default,TOMoMi:,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, can we predict what's on the exam, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.67,0:22:08.09,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:11.39,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:14.73,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:17.94,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:37.87,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:51.39,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:57.81,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:04.86,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:11.62,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:14.54,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:20.00,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:23.00,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:26.51,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
